{"tid":492050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【未來戰士】AI 也能傳宗接代？","createTime":"2017-12-07T06:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T04:33:11.000Z","uid":33072,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c33d8dafa5c5205e1e70b9f78936706708d9441","tid":492050,"uid":33072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/12/601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F12%2F601.jpg&h=f9deab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAI 也能自行「繁衍」？根據《The Week》報導，Google AI 系統 AutoML 創造了自己的孩子「NASNet」，能夠進行圖片、影像辨識與分類，其表現甚至比人類工程師撰寫的 AI 還要強大！<br />\n<br />\n由 AutoML「生下」的 NASNet，主要被設計來辨識圖像、影片中的人、車、交通號誌等各種物件；根據研究結果，在經過數千小時的訓練後，NASNet 已經能夠以 82.7% 的準確度辨識圖像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201712/20171205/601-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201712%2F20171205%2F601-2.png&h=456d152d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n82.7% 的準確度代表什麼意義？外媒《Futurism》指出，NASNet 的辨識準確度比以往任何人類開發的 AI 還要高出 1.2%，並且系統演算效率也以 4% 的差距勝過以前的 AI，換句話說，這個 AI 自行創造的孩子，比人類工程師撰寫的機械視覺 AI 還要強大。<br />\n<br />\nNASNet 高度準確、有效率的機械視覺演算法，未來將擁有無數的應用可能，例如可以用在打造 AI 機器人，或者協助視障者重見天日，以及使用於無人車上，讓自動汽車能更快、更準確地辨識道路上的物體，增加行駛安全性。<br />\n<br />\n目前 Google 已將該 AI 開源發布，研究人員期望透過民間專家們力量，一起完善功能，解決他們還未設想過的問題。<br />\n<br />\n雖然就目前而言，讓 AI 自行創造下一代似乎沒有什麼害處，但外媒《Alphr》提到，當 AI 有瑕疵、或是帶有偏見時，它很可能會將這些「不良基因」傳承到下一代，如何防止這樣的狀況發生，將成為新時代的課題。<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"http://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/2749/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Fview%2Fid%2F2749%2F&d=XFwM8SeD6i6b6mmQRHAgMW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a9b74fd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/2749/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.limitlessiq.com/media/post/image/9/7/97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fpost%2Fimage%2F9%2F7%2F97.jpg&h=1faef97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8793dc2161373b2f681ebbe3f4b83d3cb20a97","tid":492050,"uid":33072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"mola mola <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56ddffcf89c4b65aa1f4809e89014c02f39f97f","tid":492050,"uid":38528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"NASNet &gt; 進化去skynet<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3face476a7424800e92f3148c7ff492110cfe2","tid":492050,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"AI寫AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbba97ae200fd09b4df081bb670ee2fe952eb69f","tid":492050,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:46:08.000Z","msg":"AI同AI搞野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2270f2897d5d1e8b368604f2a89e910e5e1cf138","tid":492050,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"ai寫ai 愈寫愈勁"},{"pid":"da906a6d8b57d3825079f020776bb1f29ecb13d9","tid":492050,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"啲programme 識左右互搏真係好撚屈機"},{"pid":"a3a46cd9fc791d62ecf3f62fb7ece8a04349ab67","tid":492050,"uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"It狗要失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbca83f148be115db720d80151cf143b4e3ddad","tid":492050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike"